{
  "stem": "521.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I also knew, if I'm going to go down to Todd, and there is going to be another Hungarian there, and I'm circumcised-- in case I'm going to go to sleep-- I'm not going to survive the morning.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said, thank you very much, and I went back to the rest of the kids and-- kids.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a man I've always-- everybody had to have somebody, at least another man with whom you were in a buddy relation so you could help each other.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I was giving some of the apples to him and half of the bread.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We have put the apple on a stick, and we have been frying it on-- on-- on-- on-- on on an open fire, and it was very, very sweet.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It lasted for about two or three days, and after that there was, again, nothing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I have eaten the lucerne.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was very sweet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know if it would be sweet today, but it was very sweet at that time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they have thrown another apple down, and the Jews were killing each other.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were milling, you know, and they were stepping on each other.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when-- of course, I didn't participate in this business because I was not interested to kill or trample on another Jew.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe, if maybe you could get an apple.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But there were other people who were brothers or very good friends, they were looking the position.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One said I want to be 10-- one, two, three-- and there's going to be there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If I die, he's going to die.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If I survive, he's going to survive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The other one said, I want to be five, and he's going to be the tenth.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
